Text:"<s923></s><fArial Black><s1846>We Mwathani Ngai, munene iguru, 
Ngai Ithe kîhoti, Ithe kihoti othe.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s923></s><fArial Black><s1846>Ukumio iguru kwa Ngai) (Ukumio), na uiguani uuke guku </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>thî, kurî andu a wendi mwega nî tugugukumia x2.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s923></s><fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani Mwana wa, mumwe Yesu Kristo, Mwathani ndurume, ya Ngai Mwana wa Ithe.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s923></s><fArial Black><s1846> We uthengagia mehia, ma thî utuiguîre tha, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>we uthengagia mehia, ma thî igua ithaitha riitu.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s923></s><fArial Black><s1846>Ukumio iguru kwa Ngai) (Ukumio), na uiguani uuke guku </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>thî, kurî andu a wendi mwega nî tugugukumia x2.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s923></s><fArial Black><s1846>We uikaire urîo, wa Ithe utuiguîre tha, tondu nowe Wiki, Mutheru Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s923></s><fArial Black><s1846>Nowe wiki urî iguru ma Yesu Kristo, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s923></s><fArial Black><s1846>ona Muoyo Mutheru, ukumio-inî wa Ngai Ithe.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
